Add a few tests (common/copy-relocs and tls for now) for pnacl
shared lib / dynamic nexe linking, using metadata.  They are marked
broken for bitcode for now, but can be tested with nacl-gcc.

This currently involves using the bc -&gt; .nexe and bc -&gt; .so path
instead of bc -&gt; .pso -&gt; .so.  More SCons hackery is needed to
ensure that the .pso is translated to a .so before the test is run.

BUG= http://code.google.com/p/nativeclient/issues/detail?id=2713
TEST= run_shared_lib_copy_reloc_test, run_shared_lib_tls_test

Review URL: https://chromiumcodereview.appspot.com/10006038
